text: Lycée Maurice Utrillo is a comprehensive (polyvalent) senior high school/sixth form college in Stains, Seine-Saint-Denis, France, in the Paris metropolitan area. it has 150 employees, including 100 teachers, and 1,200 students."Présentation du Lycée." Lycée Maurice Utrillo. Retrieved on September 8, 2016. "Il accueille environ 1200 élèves, encadrés par plus de 150 adultes dont une centaine d'enseignants." It opened in September 1990. ==References== ==External links== * Lycée Maurice Utrillo Category:Lycées in Seine-Saint-Denis Category:1990 establishments in France Category:Educational institutions established in 1990
